"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-how-watch-katie-ledecky-2024-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Katie Ledecky will be swimming for history inParis at the 2024 Olympic Games, as the USA Swimming star can tie Jenny Thompson's record for the most gold medals won by a female swimmer if she wins one gold and can become the most decorated American female Olympian with three trips to the medal stand.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}, {\"begin\": 111, \"end\": 125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jenny Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9993464101011638, \"rank\": 0.0006540169630224254, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.999685687458682, \"rank\": 0.0003144113647322455, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Undoubtedly, Team USA fans will be keeping a close eye on the Washington, D.C, native.\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 315, \"end\": 323, \"title\":