he will also take part in the women's 4x200m freestyle relay, giving her a total of four medal opportunities at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Below is a table showing when Ledecky is likely to swim.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 974, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Event  Date  Time  Women's 400m Freestyle (Heats)  Saturday, July 27  5-7:15 a.m.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET  Women's 400m Freestyle (Final)  Saturday, July 27  2:52 p.m.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET  Women's 1500m Freestyle (Heats)  Tuesday, July 30  5-7:45 a.m.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET  Women's 1500m Freestyle (Final)  Wednesday, July 31  3:07 p.m.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET  Women's 4x200m Freestyle Relay (Heats)  Thursday, August 1  5-7 a.m.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET  Women's 4x200m Freestyle Relay (Final)  Thursday, August 1  3:49 p.m.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET  Women's 800m Freestyle (Heats)  Friday, August, 2  5-7 a.m.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET  Women's 800m Freestyle (Final)  Saturday, August 3  3:08 p.m.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET  Each of Katie Ledecky's races can be viewed on television on the USA Network and NBC.\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}, {\"begin\": 1603, \"end\": 1614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"score\"